odule mutation. Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines pure-function discipline preserved invariant. `buildCoachContext()` extend prin `safeCtx.meta` defensive-read pattern absorb `wv2-missing-equipment` filter Tier 0 localStorage + `ctx.meta.calendarOverride` mid-week edit ephemeral propagate Big 6 invariant downstream Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13e","note":"Bundle 4 workout-preview port + per-exercise refusal flow + mid-session augmentation LANDED `429c189` single atomic commit clean Bugatti single-concern — orchestrator-level behavior augmentation ONLY (NU engine mutation ADR 026 §9 pure-function engines invariant preserved invariant). Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines + 3 methods NEW STAGE 4 SUB-BATCH 2 (`buildLightMobility` + `rebalanceWeekAfterSkip` + `generateSafeSessionForRestDay`) preserved invariant unchanged. `buildCoachContext()` extend prin `safeCtx.meta` defensive-read pattern absorb refusal counter `wv2-refusal-counter` + skipped exercises `wv2-skipped-exercises` Tier 0 localStorage (per ADR 020 §1.4 Tier 0 parity pattern) → cascade alternative exhaustion mechanism downstream Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13c","note":"S3 Guards Bundle 1 LANDED chain 2 atomic commits clean (S3.C `d41e111` session guard double-start + S3.D `47729ed` bottom-nav HIDE in-session) — orchestrator-level session lifecycle behavior change ONLY (NU engine mutation). `body.in-session` body class toggle UI-side per ADR 026 §9 pure-function engines invariant preserved + ADR 030 D2 thin scope adapter pattern. Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines + 3 methods NEW STAGE 4 SUB-BATCH 2 (`buildLightMobility` + `rebalanceWeekAfterSkip` + `generateSafeSessionForRestDay`) preserved invariant unchanged. `buildSession()` orchestrator flow `startSession()` entry point modificat doar pentru double-start guard `state.sessActive + state.sessStart` check BEFORE draft detection logic + zero prompt redirect Gigel-smooth + body.in-session class toggle session lifecycle entry/exit + nav hide. Tests 2984 → 3006 PASS (+22 net new) vitest cluster `session-guard-double-start.test.js` +10 + `session-bottom-nav-hide.test.js` +12. ZERO engine module mutation. Draft recovery `confirm()` prompt PRESERVED INTACT distinction (separate concern sesiune crashed previous). EXIT paths cancelWorkout + closeSummary (NOT endSession — rating modal still in-session UX, nav reappear deferred). Post §AR.20 quadruple violation halt v1 PROMPT_CC + §AR.21 codification origin CC autonomous Opus + redo spec v2 grep evidence verbatim inline per file/function referenced + first-attempt validation effective §AR.21 enforcement post-codification ZERO slip surfaced"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:99-archive/wiki-pre-2026-05-15/entities/engines/engine-coach-director.md#---frontmatter---": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"hsvph5","at":1778925898371},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.05601489,-0.033948,0.04159972,-0.08286026,-0.00109526,-0.03082239,-0.09663533,-0.01495932,-0.01075198,0.01311877,-0.00227867,-0.03855763,0.02163591,-0.02700176,0.01079446,0.01552351,-0.00610795,0.05500469,-0.02411534,-0.02533372,0.09076227,-0.03558482,-0.01494446,-0.0631396,0.01867019,0.01817107,-0.03140784,-0.02334881,-0.08775612,-0.20338896,-0.07911582,-0.04712935,-0.0054681,0.01621726,-0.01770403,-0.0093275,-0.03010399,0.07051507,-0.03659565,0.0386157,0.00654067,0.03753899,-0.02783454,-0.05115342,-0.0145674,-0.05532803,-0.01953359,0.01878295,-0.06396716,-0.07493517,-0.00152018,-0.04012203,0.01959905,0.05645682,0.02082809,0.02266221,0.03936497,0.03382051,0.04201367,0.03330678,0.02019211,-0.02048244,-0.26345584,0.07389044,-0.01765863,0.00283785,0.00041072,-0.04766412,0.0119269,0.00991158,-0.03069024,-0.02315719,0.00315659,0.02454161,0.0073966,-0.0337694,0.02133183,0.01635707,-0.01283388,0.00275125,0.01521574,-0.02163301,-0.0505297,-0.03195367,-0.01876538,0.00909603,0.06390686,-0.00681492,0.05070768,0.03183434,-0.05627888,-0.05983235,0.10702904,