odule mutation. Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines pure-function discipline preserved invariant. `buildCoachContext()` extend prin `safeCtx.meta` defensive-read pattern absorb `wv2-missing-equipment` filter Tier 0 localStorage + `ctx.meta.calendarOverride` mid-week edit ephemeral propagate Big 6 invariant downstream Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13e","note":"Bundle 4 workout-preview port + per-exercise refusal flow + mid-session augmentation LANDED `429c189` single atomic commit clean Bugatti single-concern — orchestrator-level behavior augmentation ONLY (NU engine mutation ADR 026 §9 pure-function engines invariant preserved invariant). Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines + 3 methods NEW STAGE 4 SUB-BATCH 2 (`buildLightMobility` + `rebalanceWeekAfterSkip` + `generateSafeSessionForRestDay`) preserved invariant unchanged. `buildCoachContext()` extend prin `safeCtx.meta` defensive-read pattern absorb refusal counter `wv2-refusal-counter` + skipped exercises `wv2-skipped-exercises` Tier 0 localStorage (per ADR 020 §1.4 Tier 0 parity pattern) → cascade alternative exhaustion mechanism downstream Engine"},{"date":"2026-05-13c","note":"S3 Guards Bundle 1 LANDED chain 2 atomic commits clean (S3.C `d41e111` session guard double-start + S3.D `47729ed` bottom-nav HIDE in-session) — orchestrator-level session lifecycle behavior change ONLY (NU engine mutation). `body.in-session` body class toggle UI-side per ADR 026 §9 pure-function engines invariant preserved + ADR 030 D2 thin scope adapter pattern. Engine pipeline §42.10 8 prescriptive engines + 3 methods NEW STAGE 4 SUB-BATCH 2 (`buildLightMobility` + `rebalanceWeekAfterSkip` + `generateSafeSessionForRestDay`) preserved invariant unchanged. `buildSession()` orchestrator flow `startSession()` entry point modificat doar pentru double-start guard `state.sessActive + state.sessStart` check BEFORE draft detection logic + zero prompt redirect Gigel-smooth + body.in-session class toggle session lifecycle entry/exit + nav hide. Tests 2984 → 3006 PASS (+22 net new) vitest cluster `session-guard-double-start.test.js` +10 + `session-bottom-nav-hide.test.js` +12. ZERO engine module mutation. Draft recovery `confirm()` prompt PRESERVED INTACT distinction (separate concern sesiune crashed previous). EXIT paths cancelWorkout + closeSummary (NOT endSession — rating modal still in-session UX, nav reappear deferred). Post §AR.20 quadruple violation halt v1 PROMPT_CC + §AR.21 codification origin CC autonomous Opus + redo spec v2 grep evidence verbatim inline per file/function referenced + first-attempt validation effective §AR.21 enforcement post-codification ZERO slip surfaced"}]},"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},
